If Hipchat server runs over HTTPS, the SSL certificate must be imported into JIRA's Java trust store for JIRA to successfully connect to it. Otherwise, PKIX error is thrown as mentioned in [this KB|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/JIRAKB/Unable+to+Connect+to+SSL+Services+due+to+PKIX+Path+Building+Failed+sun.security.provider.certpath.SunCertPathBuilderException].

Suggestion is to mention SSL Integration in the corresponding documentation for Hipchat integration with other Atlassian products, including JIRA:
